This is a simiple zombie escape map for zmod.

theres alot of good maps out there, i was playing a ze map sever and alot of people were getting pissed left and right about alot of team killing and such which is common and yet fun XD.

so i made tihs map to add some vareity and maybe lessen the stress. its a pretty basic map and i designed it so players will really have to work together. no or little room to screw eachother over in this one.
